properties.headline: Gale Watch issued January 3 at 3:40PM EST until January 5 at 1:00PM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 20 to 30 knots with gusts up to 35
knots. Seas 4 to 7 feet.

* WHERE...The coastal waters of New Jersey and Delaware.

* WHEN...From late Saturday night through Sunday afternoon.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds create hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage a vessel.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should consider altering plans to avoid the hazardous
conditions. Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course and/or
secure your vessel.

NWSheadline: GALE WATCH IN EFFECT FROM LATE SATURDAY NIGHT THROUGH SUNDAY AFTERNOON
